events.name: Born Pink Hanoi
events.description: K-POP legendary female group BLACKPINK, who has smashed World Music Charts, officially announced information for their largest world tour ever THE BORN PINK WORLD TOUR on October 2022. After 8 months, the tour will take in Hanoi where they will be performing two huge stadium shows at the My Dinh National Stadium.
